 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Full Stack Engineer Insurify Sofia, NM Job details Job Type Full-time Full Job Description Do you want to join the newly open Bulgarian research & development center of Boston's hottest startup? Insurify is one of the fastest-growing MIT FinTech businesses and has been recognized as a global Top 100 InsurTech company. We're changing the way millions of people compare and buy insurance with artificial intelligence, technology, and superior product design. 
Founded in 2013 by Bulgarians Snejina Zacharia (CEO) and Todor Kiryazov (CPO), Insurify has raised $23 million in venture capital funding from top investors including Viola Group, MTech Capital, Hearst Ventures, Nationwide Ventures and MassMutual Ventures. 
Our team is highly analytical, fast-moving, and focused on one thing: getting more people to compare insurance quotes using Insurify. 
How you will make an impact 
Work with our product team to architect and develop new features 
Optimize existing features using modern development techniques to improve speed and reliability 
Write comprehensive test suites that fortify our codebase 
Deploy to production often 
 What you need to succeed 
4+ years of experience of building full-stack applications using a modern web framework (we use Python + Django) 
Knowledge of JavaScript (we use React, NodeJS and Gatsby) 
Solid understanding of modern CSS techniques or a willingness to learn 
Good knowledge of how the http protocol works 
Experience in analyzing code performance to identify optimization opportunities 
Experience in writing unit and integration tests 
Infrastructure as Code and familiarity with AWS are a plus 
 Benefits 
Employee stock options 
25 days annual leave 
Enhanced private medical insurance plan 
Friendly office culture 
Flexible working hours 
Office and remote work options 
